#!/usr/bin/env python3

import sys

n = int(sys.stdin.readline())
a = int(sys.stdin.readline())
b = int(sys.stdin.readline())

x = n // a
y = n // b

if x * a + y * b == n:
    print("YES")
    print(x, y)
else:
    print("NO")

import math

n = int(input())
a = int(input())
b = int(input())

if n % (a + b) == 0:
    print("YES")
    x = math.floor(n / (a + b))
    y = n - x * (a + b)
    print(x, y)
else:
    print("NO")

import math

n = int(input())
a = int(input())
b = int(input())

x = math.ceil(n / a)
y = math.floor(n / b)

if x * a + y * b == n:
    print("YES")
    print(x, y)
else:
    print("NO")
